data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This sprawling brick rancher offers over 3,400 square feet of living space, an oversized two car garage and a 1200+ square foot workshop all situated on a 1.96 acre lot. With 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and 2 half bathrooms, there's plenty of room for everyone. The custom upgrades throughout the home truly make it a masterpiece. The spacious main level features hardwood floors, a large living room with a gas fireplace with black granite hearth, separate dining area with trey ceiling, and a gourmet kitchen with high end Decora cabinets, GE Slate appliances, tile backsplash, huge center island and granite countertops. Around the corner from the kitchen is a large walk-in pantry and laundry room which includes built-in shelving and cabinets. The four main level bedrooms are all generously sized and include cedar closets made with wood from the property. The owner’s bedroom offers a stunning full bathroom. Both bathrooms on the main level have been updated with high end tile, glass shower doors, upgraded vanities with granite and luxurious fixtures. The lower level of this home is just as fantastic as the main level offering a huge family room, updated powder room, access to the office which attaches to the garage, an in-law suite including a bedroom, full bathroom, 2nd laundry room, kitchenette/dining area and den. The backyard is the perfect place to relax, unwind and entertain.  Just past the tree line, you'll find a creek that runs through the back of the property. The koi pond is a peaceful oasis, and the two-tier travertine patio is perfect for dining al fresco at your patio table or the the built-in granite bar. The Wolfe deck includes a lighted rail system which can be controlled from an app on your phone. Other smart home features on the app include the garage doors and thermostat. On a hot day you’ll love sitting on the back porch and turning on the fans to cool off. The backyard is also equipped with a playground and a huge 3-bay shed great for storage of your lawn equipment or other supplies. The original, oversized, two car garage offers a unique feature, it comes complete with an oil pit and hoist for the person who wants to change their oil. The attached 1200+ square foot workshop is in a league of it’s own! This heated workshop offers soaring ceilings, tons of built-in cabinets, an air compressor, tv, three separate working areas, half bath, commercial grade wash sink, plus an extra storage area above the shop. Off the back of the shop is a covered storage area for your mower and a separate storage room/utility room. Other updates include a 3 year old HVAC system including dehumidifier and a new septic system drain field. This home has so much to offer and would be the perfect home for the ultimate host/hostess, a car enthusiast, someone with an at home business, woodworker, mechanic, builder and the list goes on! Be sure to inquire about the extensive list of extras the seller is conveying with the property! This home is move-in ready and perfect for anyone who wants a spacious, luxurious home with all the amenities.
